a#top(name='home')
main
  header
    .intro-text
      p
        | DxOrders is designed to simplify your healthcare experience.
      hr.star-bright
      span.mission Dx Orders is an app to help patients simplify their healthcare experience. Reminders of doctor’s orders, refilling prescriptions and managing basic health conditions right on your phone.
    img(src='https://www.wareable.com/media/images/2016/04/12084-79b1d9a2cf525d1d89d981b11070c8f8-1461672364-liNv-column-width-inline.jpg', alt='DxOrders.', title='DxOrders mockup.')
  // Gallery Grid Section
  section#portfolio
    h2 How It Works
    hr.star-dark
    ul.grid
      li
        img(src='https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRUv54TP0hlTAIrqXQ7ysXzJuMiVR0vSIzh6eBEV0oSV2Mljztk', alt='')
      li
        p Manage Your Prescriptions
        p Managing a bunch of medicine is a pain. When do I take them? Did I forget to take one this morning? Do I need to get a refill? Manage all of that right on your phone to make sure your doing what you need to.
      li
        p Manage Your Care Providers
        p Need to get in touch with your doctor, or even find a doctor? Do you also to need to manage a seperate visit to your OB/Gyn, or maybe a physical therapist or even a cardiologist. Keep them all connected on your terms so you can remember all your appointments with no hassle
      li
        img(src='https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRVaxRXClVzXH2nIleUQexJUNlH2XWl5KzrHN6s7ge4z1YT02DL1A', alt='')
      li
        img(src='https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRzZTxXE4IXTYoohKK9xHraTyq0wemA7UKYGYCr2YCbsIqWaOGSJg', alt='')
      li
        p Manage Your Goals
        p Everyone has goals about being healthy, but how do you get there and what does that even mean? We use your clinical medical data to help set realistic goals that will help you improve your overall health.

  // Contact Section
  section#contact
    h2 Join Us
    hr.star-dark
    div
      form#contactForm(novalidate='')
        .form-item
          label(for='“name”') Name
          input#name(type='text', placeholder='Name', required='')
        .form-item
          label(for='“email”') Email Address
          input#email(type='email', placeholder='Email Address', required='')
        .form-item
          label(for='“phone”') Phone Number
          input#phone(type='tel', placeholder='Phone Number', required='')
        .form-item
          label(for='“message”') Message
          textarea#message(rows='5', placeholder='Message', required='')
        br
        button(type='submit') Send
      div
        p We'll be here soon enough
        p DxOrders will be available on the iPhone in early 2018, but in the meantime, you can keep up with all the cool stuff we're doing here or even become a beta tester to be the first on your block to join the revolution.
